transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hi, I need to cancel my order.

Speaker 1: Okay, I can help you out with that.

Speaker 2: Give me one second, pull up your profile.

Speaker 1: Okay, can I have your phone number you signed up with?

Speaker 2: 401-486-3214.

Speaker 1: Thank you, Jeffrey.

Speaker 2: Can you just confirm your date of birth?

Speaker 1: 8669.

Speaker 2: Thank you so much.

Speaker 1: I see your order here.

Speaker 2: Let's see what's going on.

Speaker 1: Okay, it looks like all you have to do,

Speaker 2: you live in one of those states,

Speaker 1: there's like a handful of five states in the US,

Speaker 2: where your state regulations for the telehealth medicine

Speaker 1: is that the doctor has to verify your identity.

Speaker 2: So they sent you a link, you just have to click the link

Speaker 1: and upload a short video of yourself

Speaker 2: just saying your name and date of birth.

Speaker 1: Or I could have the doctor give you a call to verify.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I don't want the product though,

Speaker 1: so I just want to cancel my order.

Speaker 2: Okay, no problem, give me one second.

Speaker 1: All right, perfect.

Speaker 2: You'll be seeing 163.95 back on your credit card

Speaker 1: in about five business days or less.

Speaker 2: All right, great.

Speaker 1: Thanks very much.

Speaker 2: No problem, have a good day.
